headline: S&P Futures Gain as Investors Weigh U.S. Jobs Data, Fed Speak and Micron Earnings in Focus

headline: US Stock Market Today: S&P 500 Futures Edge Higher as Global Rate Cut Hopes Build
summary: The Morning Bull - US Market Morning Update Wednesday, Dec, 17 2025 US stock futures are edging higher before the open, with contracts tied to the S&P 500 up about 0.1 percent as investors digest softer economic signals at home and a fresh wave of rate cut hopes from overseas.
